oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hank Snow Guitar Album
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording features twelve songs recorded by Hank Snow. The songs on this recording are only instrumental. The tape is dated January 11, 1957. This tape is fifty-two of an unidentified number of tapes.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Hank Snow;
